## Dataset Notice

The dataset used with this framework is derived from course materials published
by the Massachusetts Institute of Technology on MIT OpenCourseWare
(https://ocw.mit.edu). These materials are licensed under the Creative Commons
Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International License (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0).

    https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/

You are free to share and adapt the dataset materials for non-commercial purposes,
provided that you give appropriate credit to MIT OpenCourseWare, indicate if
changes were made, and distribute your contributions under the same CC BY-NC-SA 4.0
license.

The raw PDF course materials are NOT included in this repository. See
data/README.md for instructions on how to obtain them from MIT OpenCourseWare
using the course identifiers provided in each course's `course_meta.json`.
